videos.headline: Fields keeps it himself to pad OSU's lead
videos.description: Justin Fields finds an opening and squeezes into the end zone himself for a four-yard touchdown to pad the Buckeyes' lead.

videos.description: Justin Fields throws three touchdown passes and runs in another score as No. 1 Ohio State beats Maryland 73-14.
